Originally, it was a typical village,
but that was about twenty years ago,
One day, they all suddenly disappeared...
You do not mean... a mysterious disappearance, do you?
The because of it remains unknown.
But, like the villagers, the people sent to investigate the place vanished.
everyone gave up on the investigation,
and instead put the area under lockdown.
The Last Demon Tool: The Weaponless Kid's Impossible Mission?
This wall looks terrible, almost as if the builders were trying to desperately cover something up before anyone discovered it.
Like what Shibusen is trying to do right now.
Hey, do not you think the mood here is getting kind of scary?
Can you stop saying those things right now!
There is no way I am going in there, absolutely no way!
Monsters or whatever, you know I cannot deal with those things.

Do not worry, I will be going in alone.
or even a totally different because.

I simply could not bring both of you along.

But would not it be dangerous to go alone?

are based on the belief that they would lead them to the Demon Tools.
If I do not come out in forty minutes, I want you to go back to Shibusen.
Do not even think about going in to find me.

Fifteenth and seventeenth squadron, remain in contact and attack the enemies in area 34!
It is pretty bad out there, huh?
Do not you think we should give some orders?

However, I find any kind of orders better than doing nothing and watching them suffer.
It would be fortunate if those impulsive orders did not make the situation worse.

Certainly, it would be great to be free like you two are.
how great it would be if I could do whatever I wanted, the way I wanted, and wherever I wanted...
We are not the only ones feeling irritated.

he would have been the first to make it to the battlefield.
So this is the forgotten village.
I have not felt any odd changes since I have come inside.

Like I said, I am not your supervisor.

Even though I am not your supervisor, let us have some of that coffee.
But it sure is a big key.
Obtaining a key so easily in a huge ancient ruin such as this...
No, there should be no doubt that this is the real thing.
We both know that you are running hard...
but do you know where you are heading?
Geez, you should really think about the consequences before you take action.
I did ask you what you wanted to do,
but you will not get to Medusa by just running around like that.
So, what are we going to do now?
I will use my Soul Perception ability to seek out Medusa's hideout.
Medusa has her Soul Protect on, right?
But it is different for Professor Stein.
Besides, Crona and Marie-sensei are also looking for her, right?
If I can sense their soul, I will use them to get to her.
Professor Stein, who even Shibusen could not locate...
and Crona and Marie who went after him.
So, we are trying to find three people that could be anywhere in the world, without any clues?
I cannot even begin to imagine that.
But I am sure it will turn out alright.
I think, somehow it will turn out fine.
For that, I need your help, Soul.

Do you have what it takes to wield the Demon Tool?
Was it also you who attacked the villagers?
I cannot allow humans to come into this place.
Those who lay their hands on the Demon Tool shall receive no mercy.
Then, you are the one responsible for what happened twenty years ago?
This is the resting place for the last Demon Tool.
Those humans foolishly dug out this ruin twenty years ago.
That is why I ate them.
Did you think I would let you eat me so easily?
Are you trying to run away?
I will not let you get away.
With that huge body of his, he will never reach me here.
See, what did I tell you?
All that is left now is to meet up with Liz and Patty.
N-No matter how long he takes, h-he will definitely make it back.
do not you think it is best if we went and got him?
Who would go into a scary place like that?!
Well, why do not we both go in and get him?
Did you hear a word I just said?
You were telling me the story about Mr. Pig, right?
You should listen when others are talking to you!
That is undoubtedly the true symmetr-
They just cannot see the beauty of it!
If I can reach that building...
Give us back the Demon Tool.
Kid-kun, we have come to get you!
So, you have conquered your fear of monsters?
How dare you destroy all the buildings around here.
I will make you pay for what you have done!
Black Needles... fully charged with soul wavelength.
At least let me finish this with beautiful symmetry.
Behold, you who defeated this guardian.
It is different from the voice before.
Let me ask you, do you have the will to use the Demon Tool?
For those who do not possess the will, there shall be no glory...
Who has the right to say that what we are doing now is not a sin that cannot be atoned for?
Who can tell for sure, that Shibusen will never use the Demon Tools for evil deeds?
So this is the Demon Tool of this mission?
Yeah, it is hard to believe that it was protected by such a security system.
This could just be the real thing.
So, what are we going to use it on?
I do not know that yet.
then things would be much simpler.

For those who do not possess the will, there shall be no glory...
With this, you will be the last man standing.
